data.description: This home is a move in ready, Gem! Privacy fenced, landscaped front & back yard with raised perennial flower beds, beautiful sunroom, vaulted ceilings with skylights, metal gutter toppers, new roof in April 2023. Laminate wood floor & carpet, granite countertop with breakfast bar, subway tile walls in kitchen with newer appliances. Walk in stone shower with glass & additional built in cabinets in master. Built in closet systems, Sandy Net internet, & more! You won't want to miss this one.
